|ID|OPERATOR       |NAME        |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-------------------------------------------------------
|0 |TABLE FULL SCAN|t_part_range|1       |3           |
=======================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([t_part_range.n0], [t_part_range.n1], [t_part_range.n2]), filter([t_part_range.n0 = cast(-10, DOUBLE(-1, -1))]), rowset=16
